title: APHELIOS JOJOREFERENCE TORTURE DANCE

embed.description: Aphelios does a fcking jojoreference guys, the fcking torture dance is here. Riot did something good, thanks god, and by god I mean, araki. Have a nice day playing lol (league of legends) and have some pentakills and good plays with this motherfcking beast, aphelios will dominate the summoner's rift, mark my words.
